<subSubSection id="A8D6313D22467C2D3150C0526892D6EA" pageId="3" pageNumber="22" type="notes">
<paragraph id="4BF8CD134F5515F2A2C6333C56700DE5" pageId="3" pageNumber="22">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C2A8CB241E84510BF888966A8BE06BB2" pageId="3" pageNumber="22">
Sometimes the collection from French Guiana-J.B. Aublet s.n. (BM [scan!], LINN SM-374.5 [microfiche!], P-Rousseau 5: 181! [acquired by P only in 1953])-is cited as the type of 
<taxonomicName id="63DBFECF77B6B41882A0A845664F3BED" class="Insecta" family="Aphrophoridae" genus="Cordia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nodosa">
<emphasis id="010093A1CA89EC2DF675B356D371CE58" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="22">Cordia nodosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="8EB239EDA8E39DD7802ECA15CAA836C9" class="Insecta" family="Aphrophoridae" genus="Cordia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirsuta">
<emphasis id="C3FED3D029D5564D320683D270B71675" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="22">Cordia hirsuta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. In fact it is unlikely that 
<bibRefCitation id="74CC3F673BE4DD5D1FC1ED0EBE248943" author="Lamarck, JB" pageId="4" pageNumber="23" publicationUrl="10.5962/bhl.title.824" refId="B9" refString="Lamarck, JB, 1792. Tableau Encyclopedique et Methodique des Trois Regnes de la Nature, Botanique tome 1, vol. 2, part 1. Panckoucke, Paris, 353-440. ., 10.5962/bhl.title.824" title="Tableau Encyclopedique et Methodique des Trois Regnes de la Nature, Botanique tome 1, vol. 2, part 1. Panckoucke, Paris, 353 - 440." url="10.5962/bhl.title.824" year="1792">Lamarck (1792</bibRefCitation>
, 1, 2(1): 422) or 
<bibRefCitation id="AD4E301D0765D2C3C2748D48BEB4A423" author="Willdenow, CL" journalOrPublisher="Novon" pageId="4" pageNumber="23" publicationUrl="10.5962/bhl.title.60064" refId="B18" refString="Willdenow, CL, 1798. Species Plantarum , ed. 4, 1(2). Nauk, Berlin, 1-1070. ., 10.5962/bhl.title.60064" title="Species Plantarum, ed. 4, 1 (2). Nauk, Berlin, 1 - 1070." url="10.5962/bhl.title.60064" year="1798">Willdenow (1798</bibRefCitation>
, 1(2): 1076) saw a specimen as they only cited Aublet plate 86.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7D1AB5874B59C2056ECD4ACC080914EB" pageId="3" pageNumber="22">Aublet s.n. can be seen at http://plants.jstor.org/specimen/bm000906214</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B15FA0E8B25FDE16FA9A09DF33D7CF2D" pageId="3" pageNumber="22">
<taxonomicName id="C359D0F1875194EAFCAEDA2B7321EAAF" class="Insecta" family="Aphrophoridae" genus="Cordia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirsuta">
<emphasis id="FEC0CF9B62B657E6892ED225F95D3C85" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="22">Cordia hirsuta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Fresen. 1857 is different from 
<taxonomicName id="6A2FEB55ACD6DEAFFF64CE08DDB5BBD2" class="Insecta" family="Aphrophoridae" genus="Cordia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirsuta">
<emphasis id="7E1AD40195E41FBD2208E45F79DEBA06" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="22">Cordia hirsuta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Willd. 1798.
</paragraph>
